&lt;p&gt;Read it right after it came out in 2000. Hard to believe how young I was then---12---and now that I'm thinking of it, I'm curious if it'll read differently to me today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I remember it being not quite as perfect as the first two, but still worthy …&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class='writer'&gt;by Philip Pullman&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
